# MediFlow AI — Implementation Plan

## Overview

**MediFlow AI** is an AI-first CRM for pharmaceutical field representatives to manage interactions with Healthcare Professionals (HCPs). The system features a **LangGraph agent with 6 tools**, dual-mode interaction logging (structured form + conversational AI chat), a dashboard, analytics, rich timeline history, and compliance monitoring — all powered by **Groq's gemma2-9b-it**.

---

