## AI Processing Pipeline

Every user message through the chat interface passes through this pipeline inside the LangGraph agent:

```mermaid
graph LR
    A["User Message"] --> B["Intent Detection"]
    B --> C["Entity Extraction"]
    C --> D["Sentiment Analysis"]
    D --> E["Compliance Check"]
    E --> F["Summary Generation"]
    F --> G["Recommendation Engine"]
    G --> H["Tool Execution"]
    H --> I["Confidence Scoring"]
    I --> J["Response + Store"]
```

This pipeline is embedded in the agent's system prompt and tool logic — the LLM handles intent/entity/sentiment naturally, and tools handle storage and compliance.

