#### Design System — `frontend/src/index.css`

> **Design Philosophy**: Inspired by **Linear** (precision, keyboard-first), **Vercel** (minimalism, dark elegance), **Apple HIG** (clarity, depth, consistency), and **Notion** (flexible workspaces, content-first). Glassmorphism used sparingly — only on overlays and floating panels, never on primary content cards. The interface should feel like a premium SaaS product that could be shipped commercially, not a hackathon prototype.

##### Anti-Patterns to Avoid
- ❌ Generic Material UI / Bootstrap layouts
- ❌ Heavy drop shadows everywhere
- ❌ Overly rounded corners (max 12px on cards, 8px on buttons)
- ❌ Neon / garish accent colors
- ❌ Dense, cluttered dashboards with no breathing room
- ❌ Placeholder icons or emoji as UI elements
- ❌ Lorem ipsum or obviously fake data
- ❌ Heavy glassmorphism on every surface

