##### Component Design Patterns

**Sidebar (Linear-style)**
- Width: 240px, collapsible to 64px (icon-only)
- Background: `--bg-surface` with `--border-subtle` right border
- Nav items: 32px height, `--radius-sm`, subtle hover (`--bg-hover`), active has left accent bar (2px `--accent`)
- Sections separated by muted labels (all-caps, `--text-xs`, `--text-tertiary`, letter-spacing: 0.05em)
- Bottom: user avatar + name + compact theme toggle
- No icons larger than 18px, use `lucide-react` with 1.5px stroke

**Header (Vercel-style)**
- Height: 52px, sticky, `--bg-base` with bottom `--border-subtle`
- Breadcrumb navigation (not page title — breadcrumbs feel more app-like)
- Right side: Global search trigger (shows `⌘K`), notification bell, user avatar
- Clean, no background color changes, just border separation

**Cards (Apple HIG)**
- Background: `--bg-surface`
- Border: 1px `--border-subtle` (NOT shadow-first — border-first like Linear)
- Padding: 20px
- Hover: border shifts to `--border-default`, translate-y: -1px, `--shadow-sm`
- No heavy glassmorphism — save that for overlays only
- Corner radius: `--radius-md`

**Buttons**
- Primary: `--accent` bg, white text, `--radius-sm`, height 36px, font-weight 500
- Secondary: transparent bg, `--border-default` border, `--text-secondary`
- Ghost: no border, no bg, `--text-secondary`, hover bg `--bg-hover`
- Destructive: `--danger` bg
- All: 0.15s ease transitions, slight scale(0.98) on active press
- Icon buttons: 32x32px, `--radius-sm`

**Inputs (Notion-style)**
- Height: 36px, `--bg-base` background, 1px `--border-default` border
- Focus: border → `--accent`, `--shadow-glow` (blue ring)
- Placeholder: `--text-placeholder`
- Clean, no floating labels — use labels above inputs with `--text-sm` `--text-secondary`

**Modals / Command Palette (Linear Cmd+K)**
- Center of screen, max-width 560px
- `--bg-elevated` with `--border-default` border
- Glassmorphism backdrop: `backdrop-filter: blur(8px)` on the overlay (NOT the modal itself)
- Animated with framer-motion: fade overlay + scale(0.98→1.0) + opacity(0→1) modal
- Search input at top, results below with keyboard navigation highlights

**Toast Notifications (Vercel-style)**
- Bottom-right, slide-up entry
- Pill-shaped, `--bg-elevated`, `--border-default`
- Auto-dismiss 4s, progress bar at bottom
- Success = green left accent, Error = red, Info = blue

**Tables / Lists**
- No visible row borders — use alternating subtle backgrounds or hover highlights
- Row height: 44px
- Header: `--text-xs`, `--text-tertiary`, uppercase, letter-spacing
- Hover: full row `--bg-hover`
- Selected: `--accent-subtle` background

**Chat Interface (AI Workspace)**
- Messages area: clean, no bubbles with heavy backgrounds
- User messages: right-aligned, `--accent-subtle` background, `--radius-lg`
- AI messages: left-aligned, `--bg-surface` background, `--radius-lg`
- AI typing indicator: three dots with staggered opacity pulse
- Tool execution: collapsible card below AI message showing tool name, inputs, outputs, confidence badge
- Voice button: circular, `--accent-gradient` when recording, pulsing ring animation
- Input area: bottom-fixed, full-width textarea with send button, voice mic, attachment placeholder

**Timeline (Interaction History)**
- Vertical line: 2px `--border-subtle`, left-aligned
- Nodes: 10px circles on the line, color-coded by interaction type
- Cards: offset right, connected to node with a small horizontal line
- Date separators: sticky, `--text-xs`, `--text-tertiary`, uppercase
- Expandable detail: smooth height animation, no jarring reflows

**Dashboard Stat Cards**
- 4-column grid with generous gap (24px)
- Each card: subtle border, icon top-left (muted), large number (`--text-2xl`, `--text-primary`), label below (`--text-sm`, `--text-secondary`)
- Trend indicator: small arrow + percentage, green/red
- Animated counter: numbers count up from 0 on mount using framer-motion

**Charts (Analytics)**
- Use Recharts with custom theme matching our palette
- Grid lines: `--border-subtle`
- Tooltips: `--bg-elevated`, `--border-default`, small shadow
- Colors: use our accent + muted variations, never use default Recharts colors
- Smooth curve interpolation, no jagged lines
- Animate on mount: draw-in effect

##### Animation Specs (Framer Motion)

| Animation | Duration | Easing | Usage |
|-----------|----------|--------|-------|
| Page transition | 200ms | `ease-out` | `opacity: 0→1`, `y: 8→0` |
| Sidebar collapse | 200ms | `ease-in-out` | Width 240→64px |
| Card hover | 150ms | `ease-out` | `translateY: -1px`, border color shift |
| Button press | 100ms | `ease-in` | `scale: 0.98` |
| Modal enter | 200ms | `[0.16, 1, 0.3, 1]` (spring-like) | `scale: 0.98→1`, `opacity: 0→1` |
| Modal exit | 150ms | `ease-in` | Reverse of enter |
| Toast enter | 300ms | `[0.21, 1.02, 0.73, 1]` | `translateY: 16→0`, `opacity: 0→1` |
| Chat message | 250ms | `ease-out` | `translateY: 8→0`, `opacity: 0→1` |
| Counter (stats) | 800ms | `ease-out` | Number counts from 0 to value |
| Skeleton shimmer | 1.5s | `linear`, infinite | Gradient sweep left to right |
| Voice pulse | 1.2s | `ease-in-out`, infinite | Scale 1→1.3→1, opacity ring |
| Search modal | 150ms | `ease-out` | `scale: 0.95→1`, `opacity: 0→1` |
| Dropdown menu | 120ms | `ease-out` | `scale: 0.95→1`, `opacity: 0→1`, transform-origin top |
| Timeline node | 300ms | `ease-out` (staggered 50ms per node) | `opacity: 0→1`, `x: -8→0` |

Key principle: **Animations must be fast and purposeful**. Nothing over 300ms for UI interactions. Page transitions max 200ms. Users should never feel like they're waiting for an animation.

##### Page-by-Page Design Notes

**Login Page**
- Full-screen, centered card (max-width 400px)
- Subtle gradient mesh background (animated, very slow drift)
- "MediFlow AI" brand in `--text-display` with accent gradient text
- Tagline: "AI-powered CRM for life sciences" in `--text-secondary`
- Minimal form: email + password + sign in button
- No distractions, no sidebars, no navigation

**Dashboard**
- Clean grid: 4 stat cards top, recent activity below-left (60%), follow-ups below-right (40%)
- Stat cards: Today's Visits, Pending Follow-Ups, This Week's Interactions, Avg Sentiment Score
- Recent activity: vertical mini-timeline (last 5 items, compact)
- Follow-ups: list with priority pills (High=red, Medium=yellow, Low=gray)
- Quick action buttons: "Log Interaction" (primary), "View All History" (secondary)
- Greeting: "Good afternoon, [Name]" with date below

**Log Interaction**
- Mode toggle at top: two-segment control (Form | AI Chat), not tabs
- Form mode: two-column layout on desktop, single column on mobile
  - Left column: HCP selector, date, interaction type, products
  - Right column: Topics, sentiment, notes, follow-up
  - Bottom: full-width submit bar with compliance pre-check
- Chat mode: full-height chat window with context panel on right
  - Context panel (280px): shows current HCP card, extracted entities, confidence meters, compliance status — all updating live as the conversation progresses
  - If no HCP selected yet, context panel shows "Start by mentioning a doctor..."

**Interaction History**
- Top: filter bar with date range, HCP filter, product filter, sentiment filter, type filter — all as compact dropdowns
- Below: rich vertical timeline
- Empty state: illustrated (not just text), "No interactions yet. Start by logging your first visit."

**Analytics**
- Date range picker at top (preset buttons: 7d, 30d, 90d, Custom)
- 2×2 chart grid: Interactions/Week (area), Products Discussed (horizontal bar), Sentiment Distribution (donut), Follow-Up Completion (progress ring)
- Below charts: Top HCPs table (engagement score, last visit, sentiment trend)

